snippet.title: The Texas Chain Saw Massacre - Official Trailer (4K)
snippet.description:
Gun Interactive, creators of Friday the 13th: The Game, and Sumo Nottingham are excited to announce The Texas Chain Saw Massacre, an authentic gaming experience based on the groundbreaking 1974 film.

For more information, check out The Texas Chain Saw Massacre at TXChainSawGame.com and find us on the following social platforms:

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/TXChainSawGame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TXChainSawGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TXChainSawGame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TXChainSawGame

ESRB Rating Pending.

THE TEXAS CHAINSAW MASSACRE® and all related characters, places, names and other indicia are trademarks of Vortex, Inc./Kim Henkel/Tobe Hooper. © 1974. All Rights Reserved.
